<style>
html { background: #080808; }
body {
  width: 720pt; height: 405pt; margin: 0; padding: 0;
  background: #080808; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}
/* ... 案例内容样式 ... */
</style>
</head>
<body>
<!-- 案例内容 -->
</body>
</html>
```
